{"tid":1910247,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★疫情肆虐 從事人力資源30年李女士：萌輕生念頭！","createTime":"2020-03-04T14:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T17:25:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":110,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"85794f17e26a06d6f43c5c9c68291bd2c7af69af","tid":1910247,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"從事人力資源業界30年的李女士哭訴，「我一世人無試過個市咁差，連一個Job Order(即委託其公司招聘員工)都無」，又指以前不論市場環境多壞，她都相信總有人能找到工作，惟目前的市道卻是僱主皆處於觀望狀態，或者到其他地方招聘人手，形容是「連粥水都無得食」。她更泣訴，經營之嚴峻曾令她出現輕生的念頭，期望政府體恤他們，扶助本地中小微企渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n連鎖畫室負責人黃思仲則指，其公司共有9間分店、聘請40多名員工，面對全港中小學停課多時，畫室生意大減。黃指為了支付舖租和薪金等開支，連自己家庭的開支也無法顧及，直指畫室仍在營運只是「死撐」。他說，全港畫室都面臨同樣情況，希望政府可開放零售和藝術基金予畫室申請，好讓他們「透吓氣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200304/bkn-20200304175148141-0304_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200304%2Fbkn-20200304175148141-0304_00822_001.html&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIL%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=af361c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200304/bkn-20200304175148141-0304_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e51e36d1f0967c61ec9f8f856e9511d537734e9","tid":1910247,"uid":19454,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"HR<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66930a82ee4a41f00dce79a72e032e3deca4cce7","tid":1910247,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:01:38.000Z","msg":"到底大家撐唔撐港台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1909951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1909951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"80eb34de58685c18e1c9fc707e77268d79b98b5f","tid":1910247,"uid":81340,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyT